The context provided is about Swisscom AG, not Wacom. Swisscom is a telecommunications company based in Switzerland that offers a range of services, including 5G. In April 2019, Swisscom launched its 5G network, making Switzerland one of the first countries to adopt this technology. 

If you meant to ask about Wacom, the context does not provide any information on Wacom, which is a different company known for its graphics tablets and input devices. Wacom does not offer 5G services, as it is not a telecommunications company.
